org.infinispan.remoting.rpc
Enum ResponseMode

      org.infinispan.remoting.rpc.ResponseMode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ResponseMode>
public enum ResponseMode
extends Enum<ResponseMode>

Represents different handling mechanisms when dealing with remote command responses. These include waiting for responses from all nodes in the cluster (SYNCHRONOUS}), not waiting for any responses at all (ASYNCHRONOUS} or ASYNCHRONOUS_WITH_SYNC_MARSHALLING}), or waiting for first valid response (WAIT_FOR_VALID_RESPONSE})

Since:
4.0
Author:
Manik Surtani
